name: CSS Concepts Exploration
about: There are several concepts and layouts in CSS. From them, I have explained some topics such as Flexbox, Grid and Media Query. These kinds of concepts are mainly used to make a container or page responsive. These concepts are used in different ways in different places on a webpage.

name: JavaScript Question Exploration
about: JavaScript: JavaScript is a high-level scripting computer programming language that allows us to implement complex features which create interactive effects on web browsers. We are using JavaScript for calculating, manipulating and validating the data.

name: React Concepts Exploration
about: React: React is a JavaScript library for building user interfaces. It has some components to implement a method that takes input data and returns what to display. Now we will learn about the different uses of react.

name: Backend Concepts Exploration
about: Backend: We basically use the backend to keep our website data to the server-side and then we display the data on our website from the server-side. Now we will discuss some important topics about the backend.
